nvertio.in\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/06\/severa.jpg.webp\" alt=\"\" width=\"1288\" height=\"746\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.invertio.in\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/06\/severa.jpg.webp 1288w, https:\/\/www.invertio.in\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/06\/severa-300x174.jpg.webp 300w, https:\/\/www.invertio.in\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/06\/severa.jpg-768x445.webp 768w, https:\/\/www.invertio.in\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/06\/severa.jpg-1024x593.webp 1024w, https:\/\/www.invertio.in\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/06\/severa.jpg-480x278.webp 480w, https:\/\/www.invertio.in\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/06\/severa-600x348.jpg.webp 600w, https:\/\/www.invertio.in\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/06\/severa-960x556.jpg.webp 960w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1288px) 100vw, 1288px\" \/><\/p>\n<p>It is another major communication tool for handling dedicated projects. However, Slack will help with basic project management, but it is a communication tool more than anything else. If you seriously want to manage projects in the most efficient way possible, you will need a specific solution, and Severa is one of the best. It will not only help you stay organized and meet deadlines, it will also make you look more professional to your customers. It is an essential addition to anyone&#8217;s IT consulting toolbox.<\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"4_Calendly\"><\/span>4) <a href=\"https:\/\/calendly.com\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Calendly<\/a><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-8650 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/www.invertio.in\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/06\/calendly.png.webp\" alt=\"\" width=\"3360\" height=\"2018\" \/><\/p>\n<p>This tool is good for scalable meeting scheduling. You have to pay for this tool as it costs $10 per month. With this tool, you can send a link to your client where they can grab time on your calendar to talk. Now, they become aware of meeting time with you and further schedule time to chat in the coming day. This tool saves your consulting time with needed communication and emails and also schedule calls to get the actual work done.<\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"5_Due\"><\/span>5) <a href=\"https:\/\/due.com\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Due<\/a><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-8651 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/www.invertio.in\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/06\/due.jpeg.webp\" alt=\"\" width=\"1920\" height=\"983\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.invertio.in\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/06\/due.jpeg.webp 1920w, https:\/\/www.invertio.in\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/06\/due-300x154.jpeg 300w, https:\/\/www.invertio.in\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/06\/due.jpeg-768x393.webp 768w, https:\/\/www.invertio.in\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/06\/due.jpeg-1024x524.webp 1024w, https:\/\/www.invertio.in\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/06\/due.jpeg-1536x786.webp 1536w, https:\/\/www.invertio.in\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/06\/due.jpeg-480x246.webp 480w, https:\/\/www.invertio.in\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/06\/due-600x307.jpeg 600w, https:\/\/www.invertio.in\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/06\/due-960x492.jpeg 960w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" \/><\/p>\n<p>It is a good tool for handling all the bookkeeping and accounting tasks automatically. It becomes sometimes difficult to run a\u00a0 company successfully while handling all the accounting and financing tasks on your own. In the initial stages, you may not be able to afford to outsource these responsibilities to an accountant. The obvious answer is the need for a resource that one has created in Due. This intuitive and reliable accounting system will help you avoid unnecessary headaches throughout the year and pay you faster online.<\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"6_Zoom\"><\/s